snippet.title: Witchway - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
WitchWay is available now on itch.io! http://andrio.itch.io/witchway

Find your wand, save the bunnies and solve your way out of the well in this short adventure!

Trailer - RedPandaGamer (http://youtube.com/RedPandaGamer)

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
WitchWay is made by 4 people:
Andrew Gleeson (http://twitter.com/_andrio)
Henri de Rochefort-Nash (http://twitter.com/PixHammer)
Niilo Takalainen (http://twitter.com/nilkki1)
Nathan Antony (http://twitter.com/derriskharlan)
